{"tid":1595831,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該你地唔好再理林奠","createTime":"2019-09-26T08:51:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T13:31:59.000Z","uid":120623,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"369e5eaecd771b058f280453800606251daeb1ba","tid":1595831,"uid":120623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:51:11.000Z","msg":"Quote返以前出過既post幾句：<br />\n<br />\n//舉個例，你去酒樓飲茶同知客嘈交，唔應該係同點心/收銀呀姐嗌埋一份或者同知客打交，你應該拍枱嗌：「叫你地經理出黎見我！」直接要求搵個話得事既人，不論對方有咩回應，你個級數即刻就唔同咗。<br />\n<br />\n我地宜家要示威，唔係泥漿摔角。其實林鄭回唔回應，回應啲咩同做啲咩，我地應該直接無視，顯示俾中央知我地已經睇穿佢把戲，大家要打要殺直接啲，國際都睇緊。//"},{"pid":"57e6aa4da0eb2322fad10b00a0ce8b47f97e8ed4","tid":1595831,"uid":120623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:57:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29b4f79cdd7331f272071b2bb3e9a1c9d165b1a2","tid":1595831,"uid":274141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:59:07.000Z","msg":"今日應該有咩行動?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1595819\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1595819</a>"},{"pid":"75305294bc9eb91f455a4a4fdb7aa14db982647f","tid":1595831,"uid":120623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:02:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53a7cf9bd112951d714f92ed28815faf933a466e","tid":1595831,"uid":258362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T13:31:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【全民抗戰】一次過KO  對警暴麻木 同 獅鳥公關問題（少長，但請睇晒）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1596278\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1596278</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}